Inspector Rex S2 Ep27 - Brudermord

Brudermord - Hans and Paul Tomek are twin brothers in their thirties. Hans is a successful and wealthy stockbroker who is about to depart for New York. Paul decides to kill his brother and take his place. Will Brandtner and Rex get there before it's too late? Stars Gedeon Burkhard, Gerhard Zemann and Heinz Weixelbraun.

From Austria, in German
